re outlined below. Orders can be cancelled by either the store or the guest anytime within 24 hours of receiving the order confirmation email, and prior to the store preparing the order for shipment.<br\/><br\/>If the store cancels your order due to stock unavailability or an inability to process your request, a refund will be automatically processed to your nominated bank account used for the original payment. You will receive an order cancellation confirmation.<\/p>",
